  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>DogHurdle does not collect personal information such as names or email addresses directly.</p>
  <p>The App may use third-party services (such as advertising networks) that automatically collect anonymous device information.</p>

  <h2>2. Advertising</h2>
  <p>The App displays advertisements through third-party ad networks such as Google AdMob. These services may collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Device identifiers</li>
    <li>Approximate location</li>
    <li>Ad interaction data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Analytics</h2>
  <p>We may use analytics tools to improve game performance and stability. Data collected is anonymous.</p>

  <h2>4. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>The App does not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>

  <h2>5. Data Storage</h2>
  <p>All game progress is stored locally on the user’s device.</p>

  <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>Third-party providers have their own privacy policies governing their data practices.</p>

  <h2>7. Changes</h2>
  <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically.</p>

  <h2>8. Contact</h2>
  <p>Email: support@doghurdleapp.com</p>

